# CHANGELOG

1.0.4:
    - compatibility with python 3.7
    - Prologix gpib controller implemented (major feature #6)
    - fixed major bug that caused wrong readings in waveform scales for Tektronix Scopes (bugfix)
    - adding measure functions if functionSource is given (bugfix)
    - fixed bug in electrical source unit conversions (critical bugfix)

1.0.3:
    - added documentation for lightlab command line tool
    - added a driver for HP 8157A Optical Variable attenuator
    - added travis-ci integration
